":5625,"position":0},"title":"Umar on Humility: Allah raises his wisdom if he humbles himself","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 9, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"\u2018Ubaydullah ibn \u2018Adi reported: Umar ibn al-Khattab, may Allah be pleased with him, said upon the pulpit, \u201cVerily, if a servant humbles himself for Allah Almighty, he will increase his wisdom.\u201d Source: Juz\u2019 fi\u0304hi\u0304 H\u0323adi\u0304th Sufya\u0304n ibn \u2018Uyaynah 24 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Ibn Hajar \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064f\u0628\u064e\u064a\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33438,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/09\/12\/umar-convinces-abu-bakr\/","url_meta":{"origin":5625,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Mushaf: Umar convinces Abu Bakr to collect the Quran","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 12, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Zayd ibn Thabit reported: Abu Bak sent for me after the people of Al-Yamamah were killed and Umar ibn al-Khattab was with him. Abu Bakr, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cUmar came to me and said that many reciters of the Quran were killed in the fighting at\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37419,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/11\/23\/taqsir-salat-securit